{"title":"春蚕颂——献给赵春娥","authors":["陈满平"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":12,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春蚕颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈满平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给赵春娥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的生命——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"属于春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"属于万紫千红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在理想的追求中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下闪光的一生……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是春蚕——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只心灵美的春蚕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从透明的丝中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们看到你的坚韧，你的忠诚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在用生命织出的绸上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们更了解你的价值，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"量出你的深情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命虽然短暂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的赠予是何等地厚重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿叶变成闪亮的丝啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下绵长的爱，无私的心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"街头巷尾，说着你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车站码头，赞着你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志战友，想着你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丈夫儿女，梦着你……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，一个拉煤车的女工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有四十七年的生命旅程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你留给烈军属深情的爱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你留给五保户纯真的心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上班是送煤，下班是送煤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤是你的生命和灵魂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春蚕啊，你“小小”的生灵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"启迪着无比深刻的人生……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的答案啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党员的答案告诉人们——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活着，为了人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死了，也向人民献出整个身心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月的秋风啊，请你告诉我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里去寻找我们的英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋风深情地对我说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她正奔向共产主义的光辉目"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"标……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的生命——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"属于春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"属于万紫千红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在理想的追求中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下闪光的一生……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你告诉人们煤的可贵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让火光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远照耀追求者的心胸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就是煤呀，你就是火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你永远活在人民的事业中！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}